Build instructions:
If you want to add your bashrc/profilec/etc. configurations then open up build.sh in a text editor and uncomment out the lines pertaining to HOME_DIR.
If you want to add VIM customizations to the container go the the VIM customization section in the `Dockerfile` and uncomment out that section.

```
sudo ./build.sh
```

Run instructions:

```
sudo ./run.sh
```
